Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.18,0:00:22.74,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的轉輪不停地旋轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.89,0:00:31.25,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我永遠注視著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.03,0:00:40.38,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何  我如此  三生有幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.04,0:00:46.97,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每見到水平線  便有莫名哀傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.52,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠遠地回首 過去的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.68,0:00:59.94,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限感傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.85,0:01:06.82,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的轉輪不停地旋轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.98,0:01:13.20,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠深入思考的只有  Mystery
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.49,0:01:19.75,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  命中的良人就在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.91,0:01:26.47,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠  一直守候你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.62,0:01:34.98,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠  一直守候你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.59,0:22:34.65,End,,0000,0000,0000,,為何我們兩人會相遇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.98,0:22:43.24,End,,0000,0000,0000,,一起共看如此淒涼的夕陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.90,0:22:50.75,End,,0000,0000,0000,,搜索枯陽找尋能吸引他的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.41,0:22:59.64,End,,0000,0000,0000,,卻找不出分離仍能相聚的安慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.04,0:23:08.14,End,,0000,0000,0000,,臉色雖然有時難看只要能以笑臉拂去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.43,0:23:16.74,End,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然爭執偶而有之但是也能忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.64,0:23:26.37,End,,0000,0000,0000,,只要唯一的願望可以實現的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.78,0:23:35.00,End,,0000,0000,0000,,曾經受傷的內心也將再度痊癒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.45,0:00:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人與人的邂逅充滿了神奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.08,0:00:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種刑案更是謎題重重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.75,0:00:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠遇到你真的是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.14,0:00:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的舞台是時鐘別墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.83,0:00:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件的鈴聲同時響起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.99,0:00:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.47,0:00:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.46,0:00:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.50,0:00:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.17,0:01:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盜賊集團謎之洋房事件(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.97,0:01:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬啟  毛利小五郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.61,0:01:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然來信實在有幾分唐突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.74,0:01:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是開門見山的說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.97,0:01:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我家現在突然發生一件非常詭異的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.34,0:02:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我非常希望您這位名偵探能夠到我家解謎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.21,0:02:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡雖說是我家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.21,0:02:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事實上卻是我幾天前去世的外公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.05,0:02:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨終前承繼給我的一幢別墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.37,0:02:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我搬到那幢房子以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.98,0:02:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都會發生詭異的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.50,0:02:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我還有一種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.57,0:02:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼人一直在監視我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.38,0:02:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我自身是個沒什麼名氣的偵探小說家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.05,0:02:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對於這方面的事倒有些了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.17,0:02:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我搬到這裡都幾天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.23,0:02:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道廚房在什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.47,0:02:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我一個人怎麼也想不出頭緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.53,0:02:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天才會寫這樣的一封信來給您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.51,0:02:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在回想起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.90,0:02:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得外公在臨終前對我說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.94,0:02:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送給你的別墅很特別哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.02,0:02:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於這句話我一直念念不忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.12,0:02:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您對我的案件感興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.16,0:02:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在上午十點半前大駕寒舍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.88,0:02:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敝人誠摯的等待您的消息 中村操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.69,0:03:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳等著 中村操 我來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.93,0:03:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看她八成是個二、三十歲 卻芳心寂寞的才女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.37,0:03:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.30,0:03:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我怎麼覺得會是個三十出頭的中年男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.00,0:03:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.26,0:03:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還會浪費我的這大好的週末借車那她那兒去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.68,0:03:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以用電話跟她聯絡看看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.83,0:03:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是馬上就知道他是男是女了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.35,0:03:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她根本沒有留下電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是要不通知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.41,0:03:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現在她面前 讓她對我佩服敬之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她對你這麼佩服要幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這個糟老頭無藥可醫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你認為呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.68,0:03:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是男的還是女的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.37,0:03:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 他的字很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.74,0:03:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是女吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 好久沒有約會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.52,0:04:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就開始發呆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我啊 小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.82,0:04:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要原諒你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的時候我要搭電車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.33,0:04:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這是什麼話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.94,0:04:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一家子好不容易可以痛痛快快的兜趟風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真敢說痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.12,0:04:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.45,0:04:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼豔麗的陽光下 還有鳥的鳴叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.74,0:04:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是讓心情為之而寬嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.54,0:04:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.68,0:04:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能達到目的地確實是鬆了一口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.08,0:04:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.42,0:04:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看這個繞在大自然裡暖和的灌木林別墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.13,0:04:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個女人住實在太寂寞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小操小姐 抱歉讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我毛利小五郎已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.09,0:05:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在終於瞭解媽媽離開家時的感覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.87,0:05:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稀客 是毛利先生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.12,0:05:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真的來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.45,0:05:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有話到裏面再說吧 請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.19,0:05:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我說的沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.59,0:05:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄出這封信的是叔叔嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.42,0:05:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.25,0:05:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫這封信的人就是比我小三歲的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.51,0:05:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你妹妹對不對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我弟弟 阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.24,0:05:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.44,0:05:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說繼承這幢別墅的人是我一個人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.08,0:06:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這裡實在太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就跟我哥哥一起搬過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.98,0:06:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.93,0:06:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在搬動架子的時候弄傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.45,0:06:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是傷腦筋呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是一個作家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.21,0:06:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實只是輕微扭傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.89,0:06:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是醫生小題大作一定要我綁上繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.34,0:06:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來來 不論怎樣先進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.05,0:06:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼啦 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得有點奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.57,0:06:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 這邊扶手上的頂端明明有一隻老虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這邊卻沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且上面還有開了一個奇怪的洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.82,0:06:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許本來是想放什麼但是卻忘了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.02,0:06:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆個 快點進屋子來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.77,0:06:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.83,0:06:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.40,0:06:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.53,0:07:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些收藏好有趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.16,0:07:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且傢俱跟餐具上面幾乎都有動物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看 這個是海狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.05,0:07:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐 那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.53,0:07:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是海象吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.31,0:07:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.98,0:07:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜集了這麼多東西 煩死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.41,0:07:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一定嚇一跳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.23,0:07:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們死去的外公對動物都有濃厚的興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.77,0:07:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那些貪得無厭、謀取暴利的人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.33,0:07:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些動物好得多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.77,0:07:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句話可是我外公的口頭禪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.68,0:07:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這裡雖然有不少的動物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你們這兒的時鐘未免也太多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.80,0:07:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.97,0:07:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我外公生前是個鐘錶師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.34,0:07:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐘錶師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.05,0:07:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  我外公叫做出淵紋時郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.14,0:07:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他的鐘錶做的太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.90,0:08:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家說他做的時鐘能用一輩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻兔子數字的鐘也是他做的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.46,0:08:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我外公的作品只有那些上發條的時鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.50,0:08:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想其他的是因為喜好而收集的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.35,0:08:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個數字時鐘的上面有刮痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.80,0:08:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可見看待不是自己的作品的態度倒是挺粗魯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.36,0:08:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 這些都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.70,0:08:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.99,0:08:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.04,0:08:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我外公一向是個非常珍惜東西的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.83,0:08:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要說奇怪的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.16,0:08:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不覺得這個時鐘很怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.21,0:08:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有東西黏在上面的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.42,0:08:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他可能是從下面脫落了什麼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.44,0:08:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是出淵紋時郎先生嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.02,0:08:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.90,0:08:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那是很久以前的照片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.19,0:08:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他在一起這個女的是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.77,0:08:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 她是外公一個朋友的孫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.88,0:09:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前她還常常和我們一起去打高爾夫球呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.29,0:09:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個高爾夫球袋是出淵紋時郎先生的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.01,0:09:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DEMON
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是鬼的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不是常說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.64,0:09:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你打高爾夫到一百球以上的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.12,0:09:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會被叫做是 三片屐 或是 躲貓貓 的鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.46,0:09:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我外公就是因為成績一直不是很好才會送給我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.13,0:09:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來DEMON這個字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.74,0:09:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是以前一個盜賊集團的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.20,0:09:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.86,0:09:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.79,0:09:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個只偷黑心企業的盜賊集團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.45,0:09:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個才不是叫DEMON
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.15,0:09:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是疾風盜賊集團"Goblin"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.20,0:09:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.16,0:09:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我應該來幫你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.25,0:09:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.38,0:09:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的杯子把手上的部分明明都有動物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.64,0:09:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個杯子上卻沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.40,0:09:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且拆掉的地方 還用砂紙細心的磨過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被摔到是還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.37,0:10:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要用黏著劑很快又會好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.45,0:10:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.25,0:10:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.55,0:10:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.91,0:10:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就由我來整理好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.89,0:10:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.77,0:10:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你可以把事情告訴我了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.66,0:10:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼詭異的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.03,0:10:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這些時鐘嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.14,0:10:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.05,0:10:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經十點四十八分了 時間剛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.41,0:10:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先請你們跟我到書房來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.34,0:10:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶你們去看一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.77,0:10:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 一定又卡到什麼地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.41,0:10:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你忘了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.39,0:10:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這扇門要踢下右下方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.62,0:10:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.51,0:10:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.45,0:10:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.91,0:10:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣真熱 怎麼窗簾還拉的緊緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在信上不是寫了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.54,0:10:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得好像有人在偷看我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.57,0:11:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才拉上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個地方開了一個洞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.13,0:11:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.68,0:11:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幢別墅線在該破的地方也破的差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有工具的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有辦法開得這麼漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.23,0:11:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底這個洞是用來做什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你說時鐘是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.50,0:11:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.58,0:11:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 這是個鴿子的時鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.59,0:11:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是說這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.33,0:11:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.04,0:11:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.89,0:11:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看起來 跟一般鴿子時鐘沒有什麼兩樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.46,0:11:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡不對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.32,0:11:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間一到 他就會響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.60,0:11:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.52,0:11:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時鐘就是這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.51,0:11:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  在不前不後的時候 就開始報時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.59,0:11:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十點五十分的時候報時一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.00,0:12:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且小窗子冒出的不是鴿子 而是奇怪的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.85,0:12:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.67,0:12:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看了就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.66,0:12:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.93,0:12:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本什麼事也沒發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前看的時候明明還有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.63,0:12:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會只是單純的壞掉而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.59,0:12:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.30,0:12:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我外公做的時鐘向來是以不會故障出名的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.59,0:12:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是一派胡言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.47,0:12:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.87,0:12:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你再等一下 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.33,0:12:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了這個我們還有很多疑點要請你解決呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.67,0:12:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我求你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錄影機上的時間好像被設定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.82,0:12:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.41,0:12:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我回去了就是要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.67,0:13:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.57,0:13:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋子裡的時鐘都一起響起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.14,0:13:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部一起響起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錄影機也開始動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.14,0:13:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟 是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.28,0:13:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋子裡的時鐘全部都響起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.33,0:13:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.99,0:13:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停...停住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.37,0:13:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錄影機也只播了一分鐘而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.32,0:13:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.48,0:14:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.95,0:14:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋頂上住了很大一隻貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.73,0:14:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們傷透了腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不說這個 你有頭緒了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這些時鐘每到上午十一點時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.51,0:14:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會一起響起來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.95,0:14:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.27,0:14:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是你們的外公紋時郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耍的小小惡作劇吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.74,0:14:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.58,0:14:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是惡作劇的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.37,0:14:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會把屋子裡面的時鐘通通設定好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.29,0:14:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是剛才發出聲音的只有數字的時鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.35,0:14:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有數字時鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.72,0:14:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才一直在注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.92,0:14:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是那隻鴿子時鐘或是這個鬧鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.86,0:14:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有指標的時鐘剛才都沒有響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.85,0:14:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些有指標的時鐘開關全部都關掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是你們關掉的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.09,0:14:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.95,0:15:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在謎題解開之前 避免去碰屋子的時鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是時鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.38,0:15:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個錄影機剛才也動了一下哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.90,0:15:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錄影機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.64,0:15:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.06,0:15:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是紋時郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.44,0:15:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天到了十一點就有他想要看的電視節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會把鬧鐘跟錄影機設定好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他設定的鬧鐘也太多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.88,0:15:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是因為他這個人不容易叫醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.82,0:15:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總言而之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.04,0:15:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看看錄影的內容一切真相就大白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.39,0:15:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這架電視機上面根本沒有接天線啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.86,0:15:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.67,0:15:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然設定了預約錄影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.86,0:15:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還需要用鬧鐘吵醒自己嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.68,0:15:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他為什麼要設定這個錄影機呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看數字這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.99,0:15:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個0後面有一個好奇怪的痕跡哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.86,0:16:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個數字時鐘的表面也有個刻痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.89,0:16:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看  都在同一個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.13,0:16:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 這個上面也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.58,0:16:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.65,0:16:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.69,0:16:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客廳上面的數字時鐘好像都有相同的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.67,0:16:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這代表什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.30,0:16:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 這個110的數字是該不會是紋時郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.66,0:16:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留給你們倆兄弟的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.69,0:16:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.48,0:16:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.49,0:16:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.91,0:16:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說這個110是暗號的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.37,0:16:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼只有數字時鐘時間到會響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.31,0:16:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點我可以接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.19,0:16:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有指針的時鐘到了11點也看不出110
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.64,0:16:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是上面的110代表什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.60,0:16:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說110就想到了警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.01,0:16:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.48,0:16:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.39,0:16:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.06,0:17:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是狗嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.79,0:17:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗示警方也就是暗示警犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.50,0:17:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於110的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.51,0:17:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要你們從這個家裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.18,0:17:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有的動物之中有狗的時鐘全部找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.03,0:17:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.93,0:17:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在大家分頭行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.74,0:17:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些有狗的時鐘全部集中到客廳裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.79,0:17:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那些狗裡一定會有一隻有線索才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.40,0:17:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長毛狗、牧羊狗、西伯利亞狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.71,0:17:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土佐狗 還有杜賓狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.03,0:17:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說是警犬的話 杜賓狗居多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.38,0:17:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒什麼特別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定這種斑點狗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.03,0:17:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近有一千零一夜斑點狗的電影嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.40,0:17:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是101忠狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.61,0:17:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想說不定哪裡還能找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.27,0:17:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在去找找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.06,0:17:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.66,0:18:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頂樓還有閣樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.05,0:18:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門被鎖上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.09,0:18:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟 這個房間裡面什麼都沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.36,0:18:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這個樓梯旁沒有扶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.49,0:18:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很危險的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.34,0:18:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 快點跟叔叔到下面去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.93,0:18:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那個裡面好像有人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.14,0:18:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一隻貓啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.37,0:18:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是發生什麼萬一的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.97,0:18:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那隻貓一定也會傷心的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.23,0:18:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.39,0:18:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 我看到我們再到剛才的書房找找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.93,0:18:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.22,0:19:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是人類的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.02,0:19:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要躲起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.86,0:19:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.20,0:19:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.02,0:19:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 要找設計成狗的東西哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.75,0:19:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.21,0:19:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 實在太怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.51,0:19:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幢別墅一定有古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.49,0:19:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Goblin"的檔案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.22,0:19:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.85,0:19:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.89,0:19:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有關疾風盜賊集團"Goblin"的作案報導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.06,0:19:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過幹嘛要做這樣的新聞剪貼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.26,0:19:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妖精以往的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是一些從事非法商業的黑心公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.42,0:19:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是出現在不法的交易現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.44,0:19:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為他們下手的行動太快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.93,0:19:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會被人就做"疾風盜賊集團"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.06,0:19:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是他們到過的犯案現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.05,0:19:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定就會留下相貌驚嚇的Goblin人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.45,0:20:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個盜賊集團Goblin的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.47,0:20:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在西方人眼中是壞心眼的惡靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.87,0:20:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是佔駐人類家裡的妖魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.68,0:20:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種小精靈的樣子非常古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.40,0:20:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從GOBLIN不再活動至今已經有十年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但始終沒有逮捕到他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.93,0:20:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計一共有八名成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.92,0:20:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家通稱他們的首腦是DEMON
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.62,0:20:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DEMON
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.33,0:20:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高爾夫球上也有DEMON的字樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.55,0:20:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.27,0:20:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.67,0:20:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這面鏡子是被固定在桌子上面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.72,0:20:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.41,0:20:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.97,0:20:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這後面的牆上還有開一個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.58,0:20:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後鴿子時鐘就在這個洞上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.32,0:20:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牆上有洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.74,0:21:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桌上又有一面對著洞的固定的鏡子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.65,0:21:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於上面則是這個鴿子時鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.07,0:21:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.59,0:21:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭…我馬上過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.46,0:21:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.42,0:21:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼的人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.62,0:21:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是鬼又不是動物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.26,0:21:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會冒出這種恐怖的東西呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.63,0:21:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實那根本就不是普通的鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.71,0:21:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是GOBLIN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.30,0:21:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟疾風盜賊集團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.39,0:21:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在犯罪現場遺留的人偶一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.40,0:21:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎麼會有三隻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.98,0:22:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這三隻Goblin身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.64,0:22:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底隱藏了怎麼樣天大的秘密呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.02,0:23:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會那些人偶是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.89,0:23:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.94,0:23:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.80,0:23:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.98,0:23:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.69,0:23:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.97,0:24:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.87,0:24:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.36,0:24:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盜賊集團謎之洋房事件(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.56,0:24:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.10,0:24:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.21,0:24:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回將解開別墅之謎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.81,0:24:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實小豆已經出現了
